on><option value=2005 selected>2005</option></select> <input type=submit value=Go></form><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Mon 07 Feb 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="5319"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Rogue Class Correspondent Needed</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5319>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5319">Mail News</a></span><br>I spotted over on EQ Live boards that the former Rogue correspondent, Grabbit, has retired.<br><br>If you think you know Rogues inside and out SOE is looking for a new correspondent.  You can view the full thread <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=Rogue&message.id=2477#M2477">here</a>.  The deadline for submiting your application is 2/11 - so get to it!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Mon 07 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Fri 04 Feb 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="5274"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">Champion of Norrath: Return to Arms Preview @ RPG Vault</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5274>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5274">Mail News</a></span><br>RPG Vault today has up a short preview for the upcoming Champions of Norrath sequal due out next week.  Here's a clip:<blockquote>There's good reason to expect Champions: Return to Arms will be a solid release providing many hours of eye-catching, monster-bashing enjoyment in the finest dungeon crawl tradition. Without the benefit of considerable playing time, it's difficult to assess whether it will ascend to greater heights.</blockquote><br>You can read the full article <a href="http://rpgvault.ign.com/articles/585/585104p1.html">here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Fri 04 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Thu 03 Feb 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="5251"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">New Halfling Hodgepodge</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5251>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5251">Mail News</a></span><br>New today on EQ Live is yet another Halfling Hodgepodge.<br><br>Topics this round include new Zek server, Lavastorm, and "EverQuest Romance".<br><br>Check out the full article <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=64017">here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Thu 03 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Wed 02 Feb 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="5228"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">EverQuest Vault Dragons of Norrath Developer Q&A</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5228>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5228">Mail News</a></span><br>Robert Pfister was kind enough to answer some questions about Dragons of Norrath for EverQuest Vault.  Here's a clip from the full Q&A:<blockquote>EQ Vault: How many of the new zones will require access quests or flags to enter?<br><br>Robert Pfister: Players will be able to access all of the expansion zones without the need to undertake quests or earn flags. One zone won't be available when the expansion first opens, but players won't need to obtain flags to enter. A special event must take place before anyone can enter the zone. </blockquote>You can view the full Q&A <a href="http://eqvault.ign.com/static.php?page=don">here</a>.  Thanks Robert!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Wed 02 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="5227"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">All EQ Servers soon to require DirectX9</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5227>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5227">Mail News</a></span><br>A new post on EQ Live points out that DirectX 9 will be required after the the March 23rd update.<br><br>I'm sure most people have it already, but if you don't you can get it and more information <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/support/tech_support/ts_video.jsp">here</a>.<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Wed 02 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--><p><TABLE WIDTH="94%" BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=0 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_01.gif"></TD><TD WIDTH="100%" background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_02.gif"><span CLASS="newsdate">Tue 01 Feb 2005</span></TD><TD><IMG SRC="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/dateheader_03.gif"></TD></TR></TABLE><br><!-------Start News item--><table cellSpacing=0 cellPadding=0 width="94%" border=0>             <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_01.jpg"></td>           <td  width=100%        background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_02.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_03.jpg"></td></tr>         <tr>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_04.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td>           <td             background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_05.jpg"><a name="5202"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">New Lavastorm Information!</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5202>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5202">Mail News</a></span><br>It has been known for a while that Dragons of Norrath is revamping Lavastorm, but today a bunch of information about the update was released on EQ Live.  Here's the <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/news_section/newsview.jsp?story=49981">post</a>:<blockquote>Hot New Look for Lavastorm<br>What all has changed?<br><br>The new Lavastorm is a graphical update for both the zone and the majority of the NPCs.  It gave us the opportunity to revisit one of our favorite old world zones and it shows off what an original EQ zone looks like, when recreated in the new graphics engine.  This newly envisioned zone also paves the way for our latest expansion, Dragons of Norrath.<br><br>·What about quests/loot/drops/etc?<br><br>We kept the previous content intact, but also added new NPCs with new drops as well as task givers who will happily reward you for helping them out.<br><br>·Are the new mobs indicative of what we will see in DoN? <br><br>They sure are.  The new models you see in Lavastorm are a preview of a few of the new models featured in Dragons of Norrath.  If you think the new goblins and spiders look great, wait until you see the dragons! <br><br>·Are these mobs new or were they previously in GoD and OoW?<br><br>The NPC models in Lavastorm are brand new versions of original EverQuest models, developed specifically for Dragons of Norrath and the new Lavastorm.<br><br>·Brenlo mentioned that this zone’s art rivals that of EQII, maybe a little boast or something to spark a friendly rivalry?<br><br>EverQuest is coming up on its sixth year and we continue to provide new content that surpasses the graphical quality of most other games in the MMP space.  That’s definitely something worthy of a little boasting.  When it comes to EQII, I think sibling rivalry is probably the appropriate term.  They are family and both teams continually push each other to be the best and exceed expectations.<br><br>·Any other interesting facts or information you guys think players would want to know.<br><br>There’s more than meets the eye going on in Lavastorm.  Over the next few weeks, players should keep an eye out for unusual events and they will have the opportunity to participate in world changing events as they unfold.</blockquote><br>Interesting stuff.  What do you think? Go post in our forums and let everyone know!<br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Tue 01 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><a name="5201"></a><span CLASS="newstitle">The New Zek</span><br><span class="feat"><a href=pagetools/pagetools.php?act=printnews&id=5201>Print News</a> | <a href="?dir=pagetools&content=mailnews&id=5201">Mail News</a></span><br>A new post on EQ Live details the upcoming server merges and changes to the PvP servers.<br><br>Included in the post is information about character purges, shared banks, character names, a complimentary character move, and more.  You can read the full update <a href="http://eqlive.station.sony.com/community/dev_view.jsp?id=64016">here</a><br><br><span CLASS="newsby">-- <a href="/siteinfo/mail.php?staff=Draknorr">Draknorr</a> @ Tue 01 Feb 2005</span><br><br><br><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/spacer.gif" width="540px" height=1></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_06.jpg" width="17px">&nbsp;</td></tr>         <tr>           <td width=23><img src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_07.jpg"></td>           <td           background="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_08.jpg"></td>           <td><img         src="http://eqvault.ign.com//skins/default/newsbox_09.jpg"></td></tr></table></p><!-------End News item--></center>
